2007-12-29  Albert Chu <chu11@llnl.gov>

	* libfreeipmi/src/sdr-cache/, libfreeipmi/include/sdr-cache/:
	Support sdr cache ctx flags.  Support SDR debug dumping.

	* common/src/tool-sdr-cache-common.c,
