	of macros.  Add new macros appropriately.

	* Update spelling of command names globally as necessary.

	* libfreeipmi/include/freeipmi/util/ipmi-util.h,
	libfreeipmi/src/util/ipmi-util.c (ipmi_cmd_str): New function.

