	libfreeipmi/src/ipmi-ssif-interface.c: Modify SSIF interface.

	* libfreeipmi/src/ipmi-udm.c,
	libfreeipmi/src/ipmi-ssif-interface-udm.c: Support new SSIF
	interface.

