	* libfreeipmi/src/ipmi-msg-support-cmds.c
	(ipmi_cmd_get_session_challenge2),
	libfreeipmi/src/ipmi-lan-interface.c (fill_hdr_session2): Revert
	buffer length changes from earlier.  Ends up not being necessary.
	
