	(ipmi_cmd_get_session_challenge2): Fix buffer length copying bug.

	* libfreeipmi/src/ipmi-lan-interface.c (fill_hdr_session2): Fix
	buffer length copying bugs.  Fixed incorrect MD2/MD5 calculation
	bugs.
	
