2004-12-07  Albert Chu <chu11@llnl.gov>

	* libfreeipmi/src/ipmi-kcs-interface.h,
	libfreeipmi/src/ipmi-kcs-interface.c: Globally rename
	IPMI_KCS_REG_SPACE_32BIT_BOUND to IPMI_KCS_REG_SPACE_4BYTE_BOUND
	for consistency.

