	--io-port option.

	* doc/bmc-watchdog.8.in: Added examples.

	* bmc-watchdog/bmc-watchdog: Modified default rc script to reset a
	machine instead of generate an INIT.  This is the more common use
	of the bmc-watchdog.

	* doc/ipmipower.8.in: Fixed up examples.
	
